snippet.title: The Fandom Menace
snippet.description:
This is the official Fandom Menace highlight channel!!

The Fandom Menace is a YouTube community dedicated to removing politics from tv shows and movies by calling out the current SJW ideology with only common sense as our weapon!!

If you miss a livestream or you are unable to watch it in its entirety, with the permission of the content creators we turn the best parts of those livestreams into bite-size highlights for you to watch and make sure you are up to date on the most recent geek news and inside jokes in The Fandom Menace!! Make sure to SUBSCRIBE!!

Follow us on Twitter so you never miss an upload!! https://twitter.com/FandomMenaceYT

This channel is operated by NOAH STENZEL CHANNELS, LLC. NOAH STENZEL CHANNELS, LLC does not own the name The Fandom Menace and is committed to serving this community through stream highlights and livestreams.
